Class AbstractHashTable

java.lang.Object
data.AbstractHashTable
Direct Known Subclasses:
LinearHashTable, QuadraticHashTable
public abstract class AbstractHashTable extends Object
The AbstractHashTable class provides functional prototypes and implements methods common to hashtables
